#A Gemfile stores all the gems relevant to your project
#the Gemfile is part of the bundler gem
#first I ran '$gem install bundler' to install bundler'
#Once bundler installed, you can run $bundle
# to install all the gems in this Gemfile


#defines global source for gems you have listed below
